Previous records. This species has been phylogenetically confirmed as distributed over the entire subtropical and tropical Indo-Pacific, from at least the Red Sea to Singapore (
Reimer and Todd 2009
), Taiwan (
Reimer et al. 2011c
), Japan (e.g. 
Reimer et al. 2006a
), New Caledonia (
